title: accidently put SD card in Pixle 4a SIM slot, now it's stuck. How do i get it out?
content: I just got a new Pixle 4a and was trying to transfer the SIM card from my old phone to the PIxle 4a but accidently inserted the old SD car into the SIM slot instead. Now it's stuck. And of course I have no phone service on either phone.  How do I get the SD card out (which is really stuck...)
